              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Energy spectra of tritons and alpha",
                " particles were measured with a particle detector",
                " telescope. This consisted of two surface barrier",
                " detectors, shielded from heavy fission fragments by a",
                " 12 um aluminium foil, mounted in front of the",
                " Cf-source in a vacuum chamber."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SOLST"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The total number of fission events were",
                " monitored with a separate surface barrier detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
